Dialogue: 5,0:00:51.67,0:00:54.14,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)\3cH000000\bord4.5\be1}Right and left, rift and leght
Dialogue: 5,0:00:54.42,0:00:57.03,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)\3cH000000\bord4.5\be1}Ah, don't put your hands or feet out the window!
