Dialogue: 5,0:01:05.42,0:01:07.86,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)\3cH000000\bord4.5\be1}No matter which way I go I end up in the same place
Dialogue: 5,0:01:08.03,0:01:10.60,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)\3cH000000\bord4.5\be1}Whether it's sunny or cloudy, depending on the place
Dialogue: 5,0:01:10.90,0:01:13.25,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)\3cH000000\bord4.5\be1}Sometimes there's something like rain
Dialogue: 5,0:01:13.40,0:01:18.93,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)\3cH000000\bord4.5\be1}If I make too many stops,
Dialogue: 5,0:01:19.27,0:01:24.38,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)\3cH000000\bord4.5\be1}The sunset will come sometime, it'll come absurdly!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:24.62,0:01:27.05,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)\3cH000000\bord4.5\be1}My tummy's rumbling, let's go back
Dialogue: 5,0:01:27.38,0:01:30.12,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)\3cH000000\bord4.5\be1}Let's go back home right away
Dialogue: 5,0:01:30.27,0:01:35.39,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)\3cH000000\bord4.5\be1}When my heart wanders, your smile will be my signpost
Dialogue: 5,0:01:35.51,0:01:38.10,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)\3cH000000\bord4.5\be1}Let's go back together, hand in hand
Dialogue: 5,0:01:38.33,0:01:41.02,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)\3cH000000\bord4.5\be1}Let's go back home together
Dialogue: 5,0:01:41.29,0:01:44.98,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)\3cH000000\bord4.5\be1}You're always there, you'll find me
Dialogue: 5,0:01:45.18,0:01:51.58,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)\3cH000000\bord4.5\be1}Even if it's roundabout, it's not a detour
