Dialogue: 6,0:01:05.42,0:01:07.86,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)}No matter which way I go I end up in the same place
Dialogue: 6,0:01:08.03,0:01:10.60,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)}Whether it's sunny or cloudy, depending on the place
Dialogue: 6,0:01:10.90,0:01:13.25,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)}Sometimes there's something like rain
Dialogue: 6,0:01:13.40,0:01:18.93,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)}If I make too many stops,
Dialogue: 6,0:01:19.27,0:01:24.38,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)}The sunset will come sometime, it'll come absurdly!
Dialogue: 6,0:01:24.62,0:01:27.05,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)}My tummy's rumbling, let's go back
Dialogue: 6,0:01:27.38,0:01:30.12,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)}Let's go back home right away
Dialogue: 6,0:01:30.27,0:01:35.39,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)}When my heart wanders, your smile will be my signpost
Dialogue: 6,0:01:35.51,0:01:38.10,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)}Let's go back together, hand in hand
Dialogue: 6,0:01:38.33,0:01:41.02,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)}Let's go back home together
Dialogue: 6,0:01:41.29,0:01:44.98,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)}You're always there, you'll find me
Dialogue: 6,0:01:45.18,0:01:51.58,Op TL,OP,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)}Even if it's roundabout, it's not a detour
Dialogue: 6,0:22:57.98,0:23:00.52,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Deneb, Altair, and Vega
Dialogue: 6,0:23:00.72,0:23:03.59,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Summer Triangle you pointed at
Dialogue: 6,0:23:03.81,0:23:09.01,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember that when I look up at the sky
Dialogue: 6,0:23:09.62,0:23:12.16,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H39571F&\c&HAEFBFC&}I finally found Vega
Dialogue: 6,0:23:12.34,0:23:15.15,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HAEFBFC&\3c&H61742B&}But where are you, Altair?
Dialogue: 6,0:23:15.43,0:23:23.24,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HAEFBFC&\3c&H458FDB&}You'll be alone like this
Dialogue: 6,0:23:23.80,0:23:29.55,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H989898&\c&H000000&}I looked up from the pitch dark world
Dialogue: 6,0:23:29.92,0:23:36.49,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H989898&\c&H000000&}It's like the night sky is filled with raining stars
Dialogue: 6,0:23:36.90,0:23:48.16,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H353760&}I wonder when I started to chase after you
Dialogue: 6,0:23:48.52,0:23:51.05,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H35267B&\3c&HE8E8E8&}Please, no matter what
Dialogue: 6,0:23:51.43,0:23:53.96,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H35267B&\3c&HE8E8E8&}Don't be surprised
Dialogue: 6,0:23:54.40,0:23:57.24,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H35267B&\3c&HE8E8E8&}Listen to these feelings
Dialogue: 6,0:23:57.24,0:24:02.49,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}Listen to these feelings
Dialogue: 6,0:24:03.05,0:24:06.39,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H9FDEF4&\c&H000000&}Of mine
